      • getEstimatedPickupTimeSeconds

        public abstract Integer getEstimatedPickupTimeSeconds()
        Estimated pickup time, if available, in seconds, relative to now. If the passenger was already picked up, will return 0. For example: String pickupTime = "The driver will pick you up in: " + RideLocation.getEstimatedPickupTimeSeconds() + " seconds"

      • getEstimatedDropOffTimeSeconds

        public abstract Integer getEstimatedDropOffTimeSeconds()
        Estimated drop-off time, if available, in seconds, relative to now. If the vehicle already arrived, will return 0. For example: String dropoffTime = "The driver will arrive in: " + RideLocation.getEstimatedDropOffTimeSeconds() + " seconds"
